Gesture-controlled UR5e demo (ROS2 humble)

Nodes:
- gesture_pub.py
  publishes:
  	/gesture (String): open, fist
  	/pinch_norm (Float32): 0..1 pinch amount
  	
  	
- moveit_cartesian_demo.py
  subscribes:
  	/gesture
  	/pinch_norm
  uses:
  	moveit /compute_ik
  publishes:
  	/joint_states_gesture
  	/rg2_markers
  	
Architecture:
 gesture → intent → IK → joint_states → robot_state_publisher → TF → RViz
 
Important:
- Do NOT run joint_state_publisher_gui
- robot_state_publisher must be remapped to /joint_states_gesture
- IK link: tool0

